texts.content: {"text":"1. Ey Nabiy! \nAllohga taqvo qil va kofiru munofiqlarga itoat etma! Albatta, Alloh o`ta olim va o`ta hikmatli Zotdir.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,116]}]}

{"text":"2. Va o`zingga Robbingdan vahiy qilinayotgan narsaga ergash. Albatta, Alloh nima amal qilayotganingizdan xabardordir.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,117]}]}

{"text":"3. Va faqat Allohga tavakkal qil. \nVakillikka Alloh kofiydir.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,61]}]}

{"text":"4. Alloh biron kishining ichida \nikkita qalb qilgan emasdir. ","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,61]}]}

{"text":"O`zlaringiz zihor qilayotgan xotinlaringizni \nsiz uchun ona ham qilgan emas ","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,76]}]}

{"text":"va asrandi bolalaringizni sizga farzand qilgan emas. Bularingiz og`zingiz bilan aytgan gaplaringizdir. \nAlloh esa, haqni aytur va U to`g`ri yo`lga hidoyat qilur.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,161]}]}

{"text":"5. Ularni o`z otalari nomi bilan chaqiringlar. \nAna shu, Allohning nazdida to`g`ridir. ","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,87]}]}

{"text":"Agar otalarini bilmasangiz, \nular sizning din qardoshlaringiz va do`stlaringizdir. Bilmasdan qilgan xato narsangiz uchun sizga gunoh yo`q. Ammo dildan qasd qilgan bo`lsangiz, \nAlloh o`ta mag`firatli va o`ta rahimli Zotdir.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,222]}]}

{"text":"6. Nabiy mo`minlar uchun o`zlaridan ko`ra haqlidir. Uning ayollari esa, ularning onalaridir. ","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,93]}]}

{"text":"Allohning Kitobida qarindoshlar bir-birlariga boshqa mo`minlardan va muhojirlardan haqlidirlar. \nFaqat, do`stlaringizga yaxshilik qilmog`ingiz mustasnodir. Bu, Kitobda satrlar ila bitilmish.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,190]}]}

{"text":"7. Nabiylardan ahdu paymonlarini olganimizni esla! Sendan, Nuhdan, Ibrohimdan, Musodan va \nIyso ibn Maryamdan ham. \nBiz ulardan salmoqli ahdu paymon oldik.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,155]}]}

{"text":"8. (Buni Alloh) sodiqlardan sadoqatlari \nhaqida so`rash uchun qildi. \nVa kofirlarga alamli azobni tayyorlab qo`ydi.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,115]}]}

{"text":"9. Ey, iymon keltirganlar! Allohning sizga bergan \nne'matini eslang. O`shanda ustingizga lashkarlar kelgan edi. Bas, Biz ularning ustiga shamolni va \nsiz ko`rmagan lashkarlarni yubordik. ","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,187]}]}

{"text":"10. O`shanda ular sizning ust va quyi tomoningizdan kelgan edilar. O`shanda ko`zlar tinib, jonlar halqumga kelgan edi va Alloh haqida turli gumonlar qilardingiz.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,161]}]}

{"text":"11. Ana shunda mo`minlar sinovga duchor bo`ldilar \nva shiddatli larzaga tushdilar.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,82]}]}

{"text":"12. O`shanda munofiqlar va qalblarida kasallik borlar: Alloh va Uning Rasuli bizga yolg`ondan boshqani \nva'da qilmagan ekan, derdilar.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,136]}]}

{"text":"13. O`shanda ulardan bir toifasi: \nEy, Yasrib ahli, bu yerda sizga turish imkoni yo`q. ","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,88]}]}

{"text":"Bas, qaytinglar, dedi. 
Ulardan bir guruhlari Nabiydan izn so`rab: 
Uylarimiz ochiq-sochiq qolgan, derlar. 
Holbuki, ular ochiq-sochiq emas. 
Ular qochishdan boshqani iroda qilmaslar. ","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,187]}]}

{"text":"14. Agar ularning ustiga u(Madina)ning \nhar tarafidan bostirib kirilsa, so`ngra ulardan fitna talab qilinsa, albatta, uni qiladilar. \nHech kechikmaslar. Magar ozginagina.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,170]}]}

{"text":"15. Holbuki, ular bundan oldin ortga qarab qochmaslikka Allohga ahd bergan edilar. \nAllohga ahd esa, mas'uliyat bo`lgandir.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,123]}]}

{"text":"16. Sen: Qochish sizga hech qanday foyda bermas. Demak, agar o`limdan yoki qatl bo`lishdan qochsangiz ham, juda oz huzurlanasiz, xolos, \ndeb ayt.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,147]}]}

{"text":"17. Sen: Agar sizga Alloh yomonlikni iroda qilsa yoki sizga rahmatni iroda qilsa, sizlarni Undan to`sadigan kim bor?! deb ayt. Ular o`zlariga Allohdan o`zga do`st va yordam berguvchi topa olmaslar.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,199]}]}

{"text":"18. Batahqiq, Alloh ichingizdagi (jiddu jahdga) 
to`siqlik qilguvchilarni ham va o`z birodarlariga: 
Biz tomon keling, deyuvchilarni ham bilur. 
Ular jangga kelmaslar, illo, ozgina kelurlar.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,192]}]}

{"text":"19. Sizlarga nisbatan baxillik qilgan hollarida (kelurlar). Bas, xavf kelgan chog`da ularning senga o`lim talvasasidagi kishiga o`xshab, ko`zlari aylanib \nnazar solishlarini ko`rursan. ","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,185]}]}

{"text":"Bas, xavf ketganda esa, yaxshilikka ochko`zlik qilib, sizlarga o`tkir tillar ila ozor berurlar. 
Ana o`shalar, iymon keltirmaganlardir. 
Bas, Alloh amallarini behuda ketkazdi. 
Bu esa, Alloh uchun oson edi.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,206]}]}

{"text":"20. Ular ahzoblarni ketmagan deb hisoblarlar. Agar ahzoblar yana kelsalar, ular a'robiylar ichida, cho`lda bo`lib, sizning xabaringizni so`rab turishni orzu qilurlar.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,166]}]}

{"text":"Agar sizning ichingizda bo`lganlarida ham, \nkamdan-kam jang qilgan bo`lur edilar.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,81]}]}

{"text":"21. Batahqiq, sizlar uchun, Allohdan va oxirat kunidan umidvor bo`lganlar uchun va Allohni ko`p zikr qilganlar uchun Rasulullohda go`zal o`rnak bor edi.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,152]}]}

{"text":"22. Mo`minlar ahzoblarni ko`rganlarida: 
Bu bizga Alloh va Uning Rasuli va'da qilgan narsadir. Alloh va Uning Rasuli rost so`zlarlar, dedilar. 
Bu ularga iymon va taslimdan boshqa 
narsani ziyoda etmadi.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,205]}]}

{"text":"23. Mo`minlardan Allohga bergan va'dalariga \nsodiq qolgan kishilar bordir. Bas, ulardan ba'zilari ajalini topdi. Ba'zilari esa, intizor bo`lib turibdir. \nUlar biror narsani almashtirmadilar.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,190]}]}

{"text":"24. Alloh sodiqlarni sadoqatlari sababidan mukofotlashi uchun va munofiqlarni agar xohlasa, azoblashi yoki tavbasini qabul qilishi uchundir. Albatta, Alloh o`ta mag`firatli va o`ta rahimlidir.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,192]}]}

{"text":"25. Va Alloh kufr keltirganlarni g`azablari ila ortlariga qaytardi. Ular hech bir yaxshilikka erisha olmadilar. Mo`minlar uchun urushda Allohning O`zi kifoya qildi. Va Alloh kuchli va aziyz Zotdir.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,197]}]}

{"text":"26. Va U zot ularga yordam bergan ahli kitoblardan bo`lganlarni qo`rg`onlaridan tushirdi va qalblariga \nqo`rqinch soldi. Bir guruhini o`ldirursizlar va \nbir guruhini asir olursizlar.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,182]}]}

{"text":"27. Va sizlarga ularning yerini, hovli-joylarini, \nmolu mulklarini va qadamingiz yetmagan yerni meros qilib berdi. Alloh har bir narsaga qodir Zotdir.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,150]}]}

{"text":"28. Ey Nabiy, jufti halollaringga: \nAgar bu dunyo hayotini va uning ziynatini iroda qilsangiz, kelinglar, sizlarni bahramand qilay va chiroyli bo`shatish ila bo`shatib qo`yay.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,176]}]}

{"text":"29. Agar Allohni va Uning Rasulini va oxirat diyorini iroda qiladigan bo`lsangiz, bas, albatta, \nAlloh sizlardan go`zal amal qilguvchilarga \nulug` ajrni tayyorlab qo`ygan, deb ayt.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,181]}]}

{"text":"30. Ey, Nabiyning ayollari! 
Sizdan kim ochiq gunoh qilsa, 
unga beriladigan azob ikki marta ko`paytirilur. 
Bu esa, Alloh uchun oson bo`lgan ishdir.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,149]}]}

{"text":"31. Sizlardan kim Alloh va Uning \nRasuliga mudom itoatda bo`lsa va yaxshi amal qilsa, uning ajrini ikki marta beramiz va uning uchun \ngo`zal rizqni tayyorlaganmiz.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,163]}]}

{"text":"32. Ey, Nabiyning ayollari! \nSizlar ayollardan birortasi kabi emassiz. \nAgar taqvo qilsangiz, mayin so`z qilmang, yana, qalbida kasali bor bo`lgan tama' qilib yurmasin. Gapirganda yaxshi gapni gapiringlar.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,205]}]}

{"text":"33. Viqor bilan uyingizda o`tiring. \nIlgarigi johiliyatning ochiq-sochiqligi kabi \nochiq-sochiq yurmang. Namozni to`kis ado eting, zakot bering, Allohga va Uning Rasuliga itoat qiling. ","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,185]}]}

{"text":"Albatta, Alloh sizdan kirni ketkazib, \nbutunlay poklashni xohlaydi, ey, ahli bayt!","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,82]}]}

{"text":"34. Va uylaringizda tilovat qilinayotgan \nAllohning oyatlarini va hikmatni eslang. Albatta, \nAlloh o`ta latiyf va o`ta xabardor bo`lgan Zotdir.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,143]}]}

{"text":"35. Albatta, muslimlar va muslimalar, \nmo`minlar va mo`minalar, davomli itoatkor erkaklar va davomli itoatkor ayollar, sadoqatli erkaklar va sadoqatli ayollar, ","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,160]}]}

{"text":"sabrli erkaklar va sabrli ayollar, xushu'li erkaklar va xushu'li ayollar, sadaqa qilguvchi erkaklar va \nsadaqa qilguvchi ayollar, ro`za tutguvchi erkaklar va ro`za tutguvchi ayollar, ","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,183]}]}

{"text":"farjlarini saqlovchi erkaklar va (farjlarini) \nsaqlovchi ayollar, Allohni ko`p zikr qilguvchi erkaklar va (Allohni ko`p) zikr qilguvchi ayollar  o`shalarga Alloh mag`firatni va ulug` ajrni tayyorlab qo`ygandir.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,211]}]}

{"text":"36. Hech bir mo`min erkak va hech bir mo`mina ayol uchun Alloh va Uning Rasuli bir ishga hukm qilganida, o`z ishlarini o`zlaricha ixtiyor qilmoq yo`q. \nKim Allohga va Uning Rasuliga osiy bo`lsa, \nbas, batahqiq, ochiq adashish-la adashibdi.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,239]}]}

{"text":"37. Esla, Alloh ne'mat bergan va sen ham ne'mat bergan shaxsga: Juftingni o`zing ila tutib tur va Allohga taqvo qil, der eding. ","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,130]}]}

{"text":"Va ichingda Alloh oshkor qilguvchi 
bo`lgan narsani maxfiy tutarding va odamlardan 
qo`rqarding, holbuki, Allohdan qo`rqmog`ing haqliroq edi. Qachonki Zayd undan o`z hojatini ado etgach, 
Biz seni unga uylantirdik. Toki, mo`minlarga o`z asrandi bolalari xotinlarida, ulardan hojatlarini ado qilishgach, tanglik bo`lmasin deb. ","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,326]}]}

{"text":"38. Nabiyga Alloh unga farz qilgan narsada 
biron tanglik bo`lmas. Bu  oldin o`tganlar 
haqida ham Alloh tutgan yo`ldir. 
Allohning amri belgilangan qadar bo`ldi.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,163]}]}

{"text":"39. Ular Allohning elchiligini yetkazadigan, \nUndangina qo`rqadigan, Allohdan boshqa hech kimdan qo`rqmaydigan zotlardir. \nAllohning O`zi hisob qilguvchilikka kifoyadir.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,169]}]}

{"text":"40. Muhammad sizlardan biron erkakning 
otasi bo`lgan emas. Lekin Allohning Rasuli va 
Payg`ambarlarning so`nggisidir. 
Alloh har bir narsani o`ta bilguvchidir.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,160]}]}

{"text":"41. Ey, iymon keltirganlar! Allohni ko`p zikr qilinglar.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,56]}]}

{"text":"42. Va ertayu kech Uni poklab yod etinglar.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,43]}]}

{"text":"43. U sizlarni zulmatlardan nurga chiqarish uchun \nO`zi ham, farishtalari ham salovot aytadir. \nU mo`minlarga o`ta mehribon bo`lgan Zotdir.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,139]}]}

{"text":"44. U zotga yo`liqadigan kundagi so`rashishlari salomdir. Va ularga go`zal ajrni tayyorlab qo`ygandir.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":8,"range":[0,102]}]}
